            <a class="btn" href="/blog" aria-label="Read the blog">Blog</a>
            <a class="btn" href="/capybara" aria-label="What‚Äôs with the Capybara?">What‚Äôs with the Capybara?</a>
          </div>

          <p class="caption">‚ÄúSass, Shimmer, Sparkle‚Äù‚Äîand a whole lot of heart.</p>
        </div>

        <figure>
          <img src="/hero.jpg" alt="Parker by the lake crocheting a tiny capybara" />
        </figure>
      </section>

      <!-- TILES -->
      <section class="grid" aria-label="Explore ParkerPixie worlds">
        <a class="tile paws" href="/paws"><span class="chip">Paws</span><h3>ParkerPixiePaws</h3><p>Amigurumi, capybaras, care guides, commissions, and cozy drops.</p></a>
        <a class="tile pop" href="/pop"><span class="chip">Pop</span><h3>ParkerPixiePop</h3><p>Gaming, streams, and glittery persona‚ÄîInfinity Nikki & Dreamlight vibes.</p></a>
        <a class="tile pixel" href="/pixel"><span class="chip">Pixel</span><h3>ParkerPixiePixel</h3><p>Design experiments, printables, and tiny tools that make life easier.</p></a>
      </section>

      <footer>¬© {year} ParkerPixie ¬∑ Made with ‚ú® Sparkle, üíÉ Sass, and üíñ Love from Madison, WI</footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
